readable.content: A man stands on a cliff overlooking the ocean . a man stands on a grassy cliff that overhangs a deep blue ocean . A man stands on the edge of a cliff overhanging the ocean . A man stands on the overhang of a cliff . Man standing on a rock ledge over a body of water the sky and water are blue and meet at the horizon .
